==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dipodomys
<hw>Dipodomys</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of rodents of the family
<fam>Heteromyidae</fam>, comprising the genus of kangaroo rats which
live in arid regions of Mexico and the western U. S.</def> <note>An
Australian rodent of the genus <gen>Notomys</gen> is also referred to as
a <er>kangaroo rat</er>, as is the potoroo. See <er>kangaroo
rat</er></note>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Dipodomys</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

